  "prompt": "What are some toy manufacturers in Mexico?",
  "response": "Mexico has a number of toy manufacturers that produce a variety of toys for both local and international markets. Some notable toy manufacturers in Mexico include:\n\n1. **Fotorama de M\u00e9xico** - Founded in 1961, Fotorama de M\u00e9xico is known for developing innovative and interactive toys, including board games and action toys.\n\n2. **Distroller** - Distroller is a whimsical toy company that creates unique and colorful characters and merchandise. They are particularly famous for their neonate babies and other quirky, collectible items.\n\n3. **KidCo Mexico** - KidCo specializes in producing toys and educational products that foster learning and development in children.\n\n4. **Educa Tells** - Educa Tells focuses on educational toys that help children develop critical thinking and problem-solving skills.\n\n5. **Mi Alegr\u00eda** - Known for producing a wide range of children's toys such as art kits, science kits, and other educational toys, Mi Alegr\u00eda is another popular toy manufacturer in Mexico.\n\n6. **Starplast** - Starplast designs and manufactures plastic toys, including outdoor play equipment, ride-ons, and various utility products for children.\n\nThese manufacturers contribute significantly to the toy industry in Mexico and offer a wide array of products that cater to different age groups and interests.",
